        "Description": [
            "A [Ship] that was carrying a box of [Item] was taken out. Now that choice pluck is just sitting out there. The [Client] are willing to pay good credits for someone to snag it and take it to [Destination]. [Timed][Danger]",
            "Got wind that a shipment of [Item] that the [Client] have been after turned up a on [Ship] that was headed out of system. Luckily, they didn't get too far. All that's left is for someone to go grab the goods from the [Location] and drop it off at [Destination]. [Timed][Danger]",
            "Anyone good with salvage looking for work? Got a crate of [Item] waiting to be recovered near a blown up [Ship] that the [Client] need taken to [Destination]. [Timed][Danger]And don't comm me about how you're great at EVAing if you don't have a way to fly yourself out there. Some scub with a pack and no transport does me as much good as [Analogy].",
            "There's a clearance sale going down at a dead [Ship] and the [Client] are looking for a runner to grab a box of [Item] and haul it to [Destination]. [Timed]This is the perfect gig for someone looking to de-green their rep. [Danger]",
            "A [Ship] with some valuable cargo blew up and the [Client] are paying to have this shipment of [Item] taken to [Destination]. [Timed][Danger]If I hear that this package winds up somewhere else, and I find out you had something to do with that, then I'll [Threat].",
            "Hey! Who wants to go wreckdiving? There's a mangled mess of a [Ship] that needs a crate of [Item] plucked from it and delivered to [Destination]. Interested? What if I told you that the [Client] are footing the bill? [Timed][Danger]"
        ],
        "Danger": [
            "Try to keep a low profile. Things have been heating up around here enough as is.",
            "If you run into any trouble, I'm trusting you can handle yourself.",
            "Word of warning. Security's been increasing their presence in the area. Take the appropriate precautions.",
            "I'm not expecting any trouble, but if security does show up, take care of it.",
            "I'm expecting you to keep the drop on the low. Don't want any heat on this."
        ],
